      <title>由于美国产出增长预期较小，油价小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-up-smaller-us-output-growth-estimates-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三油价小幅走高，因美国石油产量增长预计到 2025 年将基本保持稳定，缓解供应过剩的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-up-smaller-us-output-growth-estimates-2024-02-07/</guid>
